  rdf:type schema:Article ;
  schema:url &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/science/domains/information/domains/cybernetics/terms/structural-coupling/> ;
  schema:name "Structural Coupling" ;
  schema:description "Structural coupling describes the relationship between an [autopoietic](./autopoiesis.md) system and its environment. Humberto Maturana and Francisco Varela introduced the concept to explain how operationally closed systems interact with a world they do not directly represent [@maturana1980; @maturana1987]." ;
